node.title: dbstats
node._create_table_statement: CREATE TABLE `dbstats` ( `dbstats_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `tstamp` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '0000-00-00 00:00:00', `uptime` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `questions` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `slow` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', PRIMARY KEY (`dbstats_id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 PACK_KEYS=1
